  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    Answers that a student has given in all exam sessions he/she attended.
    Course
    A course for which exams are created and need proctoring services.
    ExamSession
    An exam session is an on-line virtual "examination hall".
    Question
    A single question that may be selected to be asked in an ExamSession.
    Student
    A student account.
    TimeSlot
    A period of time during which an exam session can take place.

Package cw_models Description

Contains typical model classes as in a MVC pattern.

Classes inside are data models that are supposed to be held at the university's courseware. Since we do not have access to a real courseware, classes here are all similated ones.
